		<title>Upcoming Half Day Lightroom 4 Workshop in NJ with Andrew Darlow</title>
		<link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/imagingbuffet/~3/wAPCC9VCFrk/</link>
		<comments>http://imagingbuffet.com/2012/04/02/upcoming-half-day-lightroom-4-workshop-in-nj-with-andrew-darlow/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Mon, 02 Apr 2012 21:56:46 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>imaging@andrewdarlow.com (Andrew Darlow)</dc:creator>
		
